JS WORKSHOP:
read this book to learn javascript:
https://www.google.com/search?q=javascript+the+good+parts

experiment with what javascript can do using jQuery / its documentation:
http://jquery.com/


NODE AND SERVER COMMANDS:


to start server:
go to folder in terminal
type
node app.js


GIT COMMANDS:


to commit:
git commit -am "your message"

to add new files (dont forget this, i do a lot):
git add your-file.html


push and pull:
git push origin master
git pull 


get status of commits:
git status 



